title: No Frame

Daylight dreaming

Darkness seeking

Daylight dreaming

Way out of this

Daylight dreaming

Darkness seeking

Daylight dreaming

There must be some kind of way out of this

Way out of this



Can't keep faking it

I am not myself

Selling you blank stares

I have lost my way

Lost my way



Way out of this

Way out of this



Way out of this

Way out of this



Daylight dreaming

Darkness seeking



Time has no frame!



Well I belong right here

Where the light runs from me

I don't believe in fear

'Cause this place can't haunt me



Well I belong right here

Where the light runs from me

I don't believe in fear

'Cause this place can't haunt me
